{
  "stem": "11797.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was going on until-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] --1944.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About November.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "November or December.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe even-- no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was January.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know why?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I heard-- they were singing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because it was-- it was already Christmas.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I heard that the Germans were singing in the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'll never forget that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were singing, 'O Tanenbaum,' they were singing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is something, I'll never forget that. 'O Tanenbaum.' They were all singing, in the sentries, 'O Tanenbaum.'",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "December, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then in December, they took me out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took us, another camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My brother to a different camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He went to another camp, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- my mind was not normal to comprehend, nor to see, nor to worry, nor to-- I was-- I became like an animal.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't even know what was going on in the world now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I became to-- excuse my expression-- I was afraid to go at night, to the bathroom, from the camp, you know, because they said, if you're going to go at night to the bathroom, they will shoot you.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So people-- especially me, I'm not talking about people-- I used to make in the same pot, now, and eat in the same pot now.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
